{
  "texts": [
    "We implemented new logic to check whether fake edges are needed.",
    "When a user commands a merge operation, we first check if there is a path in the local supervoxel graph.",
    "If there is, we extract all local edges between the two components that are being merged and process the merge operation with them.",
    "If there are no such edges, the original user input is used to insert a fake edge between the two selected supervoxels.",
    "Common format for all supervoxel graphs."
  ]
}